703624f-b.text:
Classon Avenue, north from St. Johns Place. On the east side of the avenue are St. Theressa Auditorium school and church (F. C.)
View 2 shows St. Theressa Church, seen from Park Place.
View 3 is north from near the church.

P.L. Sperr            September 14, 1941
No Reproductions      Views 1-5
